Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathing out as I sink to the bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I breathe out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and though I feel heavy as I leave\Nmy floatie of a body behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am being freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked up at the bubbles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,as I let myself sink\Nuntil my back touched the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Swoosh, swoosh, swoosh, swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...\NSneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Swoosh, swoosh, swoosh, swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Distance"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I'm thinking about stopping by\Nyour place today... You mind??!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Adachi, can you do sit-ups???"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Adachi, can you do sit-ups???"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What even was that message just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's exactly how it sounds...\NI-I was wondering if you can do sit-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I just did one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing. You see, I can't do any\Nunless someone holds down my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. That's it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck was that conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, yup, yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? You just walked for five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly. At least get\Nthe most out of this trial voucher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you been\Ngoing to school every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You see me leave every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean\Nyou're actually going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that's going\Nto suffer if you don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always taught you not to be a burden\Nto those around you, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said I know and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being a burden to others
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one thing my mom\Nhad always drilled into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she feared that I'd end up\Na good-for-nothing in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, is the fact that I'm\Nfloating here actually burdening anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when I'm skipping school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just escaping being in\Na classroom because it feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck at the bottom of a well\Nand can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Classes will continue even if I'm not there,\Nwithout a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking up at the water's surface,\Nit turned everything blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminded of the label of\Nthe mineral water Adachi drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a brilliant shade of aqua.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, just that color and the reflections
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I joined this gym...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even I get some\Nexcellent ideas at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--We did that last week!\N--I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is filled with grandpas and grandmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so even someone my age gets to enjoy\Nbeing the youngest and feeling superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you had to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm getting at, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding. But it is rare\Nto see someone young like you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't know you were here, Ms. Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well, hello, Ms. Shimada
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... So this is destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan is tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--Who would've thought I'd run\Ninto Adachi's mom in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,--That coach is just awful.\N--Who would've thought I'd run\Ninto Adachi's mom in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,--Right? The other one's so much better.\NAnd they sound better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,--Adachi hates talking about her parents.\N--Right? The other one's so much better.\NAnd they sound better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,--Her lips tighten and she never really\Ntalks about them.\N--Right? The other one's so much better.\NAnd they sound better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're absolutely right.\NBeing younger isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--I don't feel any warmth in how\NAdachi feels about her parents.\N--You're absolutely right.\NBeing younger isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how old is your daughter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's 15. A first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then things must be easier\Nnow that entrance exams are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They are, but she's such a troublemaker.\NI just don't know what to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She at least goes to school,\Nbut who knows if she's actually trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She never says what she's thinking.\NI just don't get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a depressing child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... know Ada... your daughter very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe you shouldn't\Ntalk about her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you don't understand her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because you haven't actually\Ntried to understand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,--Who do you--?\N--I'm not trying to start an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here with a parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That really has nothing to do with this.\NThey're not going to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't exactly know what's right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's have a competition\Nto decide what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever can stay in the sauna longer wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So just for today, I ask that you actually\Nbe a good mom to your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your way of being defiant or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it's been.\NThe ringing in my ears is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Adachi could never even imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that her mom and her classmate were
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,childishly duking it out in the sauna right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly is a good mom to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know because I've never been a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me your ideal then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think just a normal mom would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like being with your kid and\Nhaving dinner with them, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to let you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to let me win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's actually happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's actually happy,\NI wish she'd just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She just shuts herself off from everyone,\Nno matter where I take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea if she's having fun or anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She was probably five? Oh, maybe four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you thinking about the past?\NWhy not think about your daughter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one likes listening\Nto their mother at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go ahead let you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well. Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't this happen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But last time, you were doing this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your legs seem to keep twitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Yup. It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So yesterday... My mom was being weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She was weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We had dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird... and sort of nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But also suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She always makes food for me,\Nbut we never eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's rarely ever home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I was so anxious that I had\Nno idea what the food tasted like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what all that was about though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that I have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're c-close...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I really can smell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Adachi, do some sit-ups for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sit-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see up your skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did I do something wrong?\NI was just trying to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! I was the only one who saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because that you saw\Nthat it's... you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess you can't do any sit-ups, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... was that supposed to be a sit-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess nothing can ever change in just a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed she seemed to be emitting the\Nsame kind of wavelengths as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's your little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This little weirdo is Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my friend, or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. A token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have half, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nom, nom... Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister ended up naming\Nher peculiar friend "Yachi."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Karaoke, getting something to eat,\Nor the river..."\N"Where do you want to go???"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Karaoke, getting something to eat,\Nor the river..."\N"Where do you want to go???"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Shimamura? What's this message about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked karaoke.\NNagafuji wanted to eat somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hino wanted to go to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hino invited me out next Sunday,\Nso I figured I'd invite you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see... But wouldn't I make things awkward?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you actually worry about stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I figured you probably\Ndidn't care about harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, I guess you're coming then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So wait, are we going to end up\Ngoing wherever I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Then karaoke, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go ahead and tell Hino and Nagafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's-- O-Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... Let's sing something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure... What should we sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Something you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Post Office"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always late to class,\Nbut you're actually on time to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how I feel hearing that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Hair's not here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? H-Hey, did you buy that outfit\Nat Shimamura? It looks great on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize everyone makes that joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been great if you\Nwore your work outfit, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd actually show up, Adacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... Well, I had nothing better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. You were bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You either sound like a high school kid\Nor death with that motive, so I approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Adacchi, let's totes have fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Adacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Adacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess I'll get things started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ The void of time... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess I'll actually put in a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Song Requests"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Dandelion"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind having fun with everyone\Nlike this, but something feels off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also seems like Shimamura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is forcing herself to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking back on her in a daze\Non the second floor of the gym...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That seemed more normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Shimamura and I have\Nthe difference of being good or bad at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we pretty much feel the same\Nwhen it comes to hanging out with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fact that we're so similar with that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,makes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we're going in order, it should be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I get another mic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Adachi and I are going to sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Adacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Adacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Song Name: {\i1}Merry-go-round{\i0}"\N"Send"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be helping me out if you sang with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like singing in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I'm with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Round and round goes the merry-go-round{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I want to reach you, but I just can't{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Will there ever be a day that we'll overlap?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I hope you feel the same way, too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:19:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}It's like the middle of a donut{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}You think there's something there,{\i0}\N{\i1}but it's nowhere to be found{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}The sweeter it gets, the more I want to peek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}The moment I casually got on board,{\i0}\N{\i1}the bell rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I stared at you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I was just staring off into the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Because we'll get dizzy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}All sparkly and all fluffy, we get closer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun, Adacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'd rather you just say my name normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like nicknames?\NWait, why am I the only one not allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, turn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't your house to the left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}But how do you feel about me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't have your usual mineral water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice and breezy near your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the view amazing, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like doing stuff like that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um... maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't invite you anymore if you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm not suffering or anything,\Nso please invite me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it seemed like you had\Nsomething you wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept looking at me at karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I staring that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think you were just imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our eyes met so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bunch of things\NI want to say to Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I said any of them,\NI feel like she'd look at me weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or she'd run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all things like that,\Nso I just shrink back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And they just keep piling up...\Nand become stagnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a bunch of things\Njust dog-pile above my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when a fruit ripens and gathers nutrients,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but after some time,\Nit rots and falls to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a sapling sticking out of the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the end peeks out and tries to escape my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I held it back, but I was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:22:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you pat me on the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even look up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I overcame these feelings of regrets mixed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with something else many times and despaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, I still looked forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you like being coddled, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like time and the Earth had just\Ncome to a stop and were staring at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how fast my heart was beating,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart was so calm\NI almost wanted to cry softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy right now from a girl\Nfrom my class patting me on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with me? Am I stupid? Am I weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's actually a little bit of both...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Big Sis in class, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, give me your can.\NI'll go throw it away for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's still some left.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied. The can was actually empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be someone special to Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean that in a weird way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I actually was special to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.93,0:23:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 4: 'High School Girls On Holiday'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 4: 'High School Girls On Holiday'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to the realization\Nthat I guess I really do like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 4: 'High School Girls On Holiday'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi's Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi's Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment when you're singing your\Nheart out and the employee comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi's Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Clack. Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! The real employee just showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--Er, I...\N--Wow, it's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.01,0:24:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--Seriously...\N--It's the employee, Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your point?!
